Package: tlstractor
Title: Transfer Learning of Summary Statistics to Tractor
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Wenxuan",
      family = "Lu",
      email = "wenxuanlu@hotmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0000-0985-2291")
    )
  )
Description: Implements TLS-Tractor, a transfer-learning framework for
  local ancestry-aware genome-wide association studies (GWAS) in admixed
  populations. TLS-Tractor combines internal individual-level data with
  external standard GWAS summary statistics to improve ancestry-specific
  effect estimation and overall association testing in the Tractor framework.
